text: Mimusops is a genus of plant. It is in the family Sapotaceae. == Species == Some species in this genus are: * Mimusops acutifolia, Mildbr. * Mimusops angel, Chiov. * Mimusops commersonii * Mimusops caffra * Mimusops elengi * Mimusops heckelii - African Cherry, Baku, Douka, Makore, Ukola * Mimusops obovata * Mimusops penduliflora, Engl. * Mimusops petiolaris * Mimusops riparia, Engl. * Mimusops sechellarum, (Oliv.) Hemsl. * Mimusops zeyheri ==References== * Allaby, Michael. 1998. A Dictionary of Plant Sciences. Oxford University Press, New York Category:Sapotaceae
title: Mimusops
